title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jul 8 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jul 8 2022
description:
Singer Macy Gray comes out strong for biological women, and quickly walks it back after social media outrage. Biology is real. Headline: When a quarter of the class identifies as transgender. Karine Jean-Pierre says Biden is fine with pro-abortion activists protesting outside the restaurant where Justice Brett Kavanaugh was eating. Julie Kelly, senior contributor to American Greatness and author of "January 6: How Democrats Used the Capitol Protest to Launch a War on Terror Against the Political Right," joins Clay and Buck to discuss the illegal treatment of January 6th trespassers. Streaming show recommendations: Stranger Things, Peaky Blinders, and The Boys.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
